  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add caraway seeds, cumin seeds, ground cumin, ground coriander, salt, and black pepper. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add brown lentils and stir to coat with spice mixture.",
    "Add water to the saucepan and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low, cover, and simmer for 25 minutes, or until lentils are tender.",
    "Stir in chopped parsley and serve hot.",
    "Serve over rice or with some crusty bread."
